### Test Vendoor Enhanced Scraping
### Make sure server is running on http://localhost:5000

### 1. Start Scraping (Save to JSON)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/vendoor/scrape-and-save
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "your-vendoor-email@example.com",
  "password": "your-vendoor-password",
  "maxPages": 2,
  "format": "json",
  "includeDetails": false
}

###

### 2. Check Progress
GET http://localhost:5000/api/vendoor/enhanced-progress

###

### 3. List Export Files
GET http://localhost:5000/api/vendoor/files

###

### 4. Download File (replace filename)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/vendoor/download/vendoor_products_2025-01-27T18-30-45.json

###

### 5. Delete File (replace filename)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/vendoor/files/vendoor_products_2025-01-27T18-30-45.json

###

### Test with CSV format
POST http://localhost:5000/api/vendoor/scrape-and-save
